'''卡罗琳·班伯格·富尔德'''（{{lang-en|Caroline Bamberger Frank Fuld}}，{{bd|1864年|3月16日|1944年|7月18日}}）是一位[[美国犹太人|美国犹太]]女百货商人和慈善家，和她哥哥[[路易斯·班伯格|路易斯·班伯格]]通过资助建立了[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[普林斯頓|普林斯顿市]]的[[普林斯顿高等研究院|普林斯顿高等研究院]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://knowingnewark.npl.org/an-enlightened-life-of-selling-and-giving/|title=An Enlightened Life of Selling and Giving|last=impressM|website=Charles Cummings|access-date=2019-04-28|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428192854/https://knowingnewark.npl.org/an-enlightened-life-of-selling-and-giving/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FM-QDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA76&dq=wor+bamberger's+6th+floor&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjKxKCTvvPhAhVST98KHUyaDZ0Q6AEIKjAA#v=onepage&q=wor&f=false|title=Louis Bamberger: Department Store Innovator and Philanthropist|last=Forgosh|first=Linda B.|date=2016-09-06|publisher=Brandeis University Press|isbn=9781611689822|language=en|access-date=2020-11-07|archive-date=2020-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314050637/https://books.google.com/books?id=FM-QDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA76&dq=wor+bamberger%27s+6th+floor&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjKxKCTvvPhAhVST98KHUyaDZ0Q6AEIKjAA#v=onepage&q=wor&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://knowingnewark.npl.org/an-enlightened-life-of-selling-and-giving/|title=An Enlightened Life of Selling and Giving|last=impressM|website=Charles Cummings|access-date=2019-04-28|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428192854/https://knowingnewark.npl.org/an-enlightened-life-of-selling-and-giving/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

